1
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:09,420
♪By the small window♪

2
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:13,260
♪She is grooming herself♪

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:19,860
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

4
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,180
♪Through willows glows the sinking sun♪

5
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,980
♪Over walls so still and bare♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,900
♪A few faint strokes remain,
shadows of words♪

7
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:33,500
♪In my twilight years,
I yearn for what is lost♪

8
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:36,420
♪I try not to remember♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,620
♪How far we were apart♪

10
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:47,620
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:54,740
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

12
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,100
♪Now I gaze alone at the full moon,
entranced by its wistful beauty♪

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,980
[Agarwood Like a Dream]

14
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
[Episode 8]

15
00:01:08,100 --> 00:01:09,020
Let Doukou do it.

16
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:10,060
Don't move.

17
00:01:22,940 --> 00:01:23,980
You're mine.

18
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:25,620
Surely I'm allowed to see you?

19
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:27,620
Don't forget

20
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:32,620
that Ms. Bai wanted you
to let Grandmother deal with me.

21
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:44,500
Since you just hit me
in front of everyone,

22
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:47,820
why bother treating my wounds now?

23
00:01:48,220 --> 00:01:49,500
If I hadn't stepped in,

24
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:51,500
you'd be dead by now.

25
00:01:52,020 --> 00:01:53,260
Grandmother knows it well

26
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:56,020
that I just wanted her to let you off.

27
00:01:58,700 --> 00:01:59,820
You trust me?

28
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:01,460
From the day we met,

29
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:03,100
we've faced countless dangers together

30
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:04,940
and I've never doubted you.

31
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:06,940
All that matters is that you are safe.

32
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:13,500
If you truly trust me,

33
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:15,300
then why did you hit me?

34
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:22,620
I'm sorry.

35
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:27,580
I know

36
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:30,620
that if you keep defying Grandmother,

37
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,140
it'll end badly for me.

38
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:01,900
Master,

39
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,940
his lips are too tight.

40
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:07,700
I've made sure
your wife and children are safe,

41
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:09,940
and I'll get
the best physician in Shangjing

42
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:13,060
to treat your mother's legs.

43
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:14,820
Can you confess now?

44
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:18,620
Please, sir, don't harm my family.

45
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,540
I'll confess to everything.

46
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:20,900
It was Ms. Bai

47
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:22,140
who gave me the orders.

48
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:29,980
Buhan.

49
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:31,020
All of you, get out.

50
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,060
Get out!

51
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:34,860
Buhan,

52
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,860
what's going on here?

53
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:38,980
I warned you when Rumeng was sold

54
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:40,180
to the pleasure house last time.

55
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:42,700
Did I not make myself clear?

56
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:43,380
I...

57
00:03:43,380 --> 00:03:45,260
I don't understand
what you're trying to say.

58
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:50,060
Do you understand now?

59
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:51,060
Buhan,

60
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:56,700
I am your lawfully wedded wife, Ms. Bai.

61
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,660
I'll say this one last time.

62
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,540
I only have eyes for Rumeng,

63
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:03,900
and I won't allow you to hurt her again.

64
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:04,820
Do you hear me?

65
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,380
I didn't hurt her.

66
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,500
I didn't.

67
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,420
I'm sorry.

68
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:16,500
It won't happen again.

69
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:18,100
You'd better be genuinely sorry.

70
00:04:18,860 --> 00:04:20,500
If she's hurt in the slightest way,

71
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:23,700
I'll kill you.

72
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:41,500
Her Highness is willing
to give you another chance,

73
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:43,860
but you must make
the incense she desires,

74
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:45,540
Nan Qing.

75
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:51,920
[Incense Pact]

76
00:04:53,580 --> 00:04:56,060
What exactly does Her Highness want?

77
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:10,740
Soothing incense.

78
00:05:42,820 --> 00:05:44,700
Mr. Nan Qing, you visit
the Wengong Mansion so often.

79
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:47,220
You truly are a favorite
of Her Highness.

80
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:13,580
Master,

81
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:15,100
the young lady has returned.

82
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:18,900
Ye Buhan threatened me with a knife.

83
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:21,020
He's now messing with the Bai family.

84
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:22,940
Does he still respect you
as the head of the Bai family?

85
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:25,780
You brought this upon yourself.

86
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:28,300
It was you who caused the trouble
for Her Highness, wasn't it?

87
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:29,660
Do you even realize

88
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:31,860
the kind of disaster
this will bring to the Bai family?

89
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:36,260
I don't know what you are talking about.

90
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:39,260
Are you sure?

91
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:43,260
The messenger, Sheng,
has already confessed.

92
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:45,700
After months of planning,

93
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:47,460
the eyes and ears I had in the Ye family
are no longer of any use.

94
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:49,660
Don't resort to such despicable tactics

95
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:51,860
as those foolish women do again.

96
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,340
I'm simply worried that...

97
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:57,200
You're just worried

98
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,620
about being kicked out of the Ye family,
aren't you?

99
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:01,460
Since Madam Ye has approved of you,

100
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:04,220
all you need to do
is reclaim control of the family.

101
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:07,020
This will help us
acquire Qixiang Pavilion smoothly.

102
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:09,860
In the future, don't engage
in any unnecessary actions

103
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:11,540
that could disrupt our plans.

104
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:13,900
The pleasure house,

105
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:16,260
the assassination,

106
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:17,860
and the matter concerning Her Highness.

107
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:20,940
She's gotten away from all of them.

108
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,460
Was it your doing, Master?

109
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:26,220
Life is like a dream.

110
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:28,100
How long can one enjoy happiness?

111
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,460
Only the beauty

112
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:32,940
is what I yearn for.

113
00:07:50,570 --> 00:07:53,770
♪By the small window♪

114
00:07:54,210 --> 00:07:57,410
♪She is grooming herself♪

115
00:07:57,770 --> 00:08:04,130
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

116
00:08:04,410 --> 00:08:06,370
♪Through willows glows the sinking sun♪

117
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:08,090
♪Over walls so still and bare♪

118
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:11,250
♪A few faint strokes remain,
shadows of words♪

119
00:08:11,370 --> 00:08:13,660
♪In my twilight years,
I yearn for what is lost♪

120
00:08:13,660 --> 00:08:14,580
Hold on,

121
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,180
I'll put it on for you.

122
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:19,060
♪I try not to remember♪

123
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:19,940
What's the matter, Buhan?

124
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:21,620
You look great. Let's go.

125
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:24,810
♪How far we were apart♪

126
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:26,740
Come with me.

127
00:08:26,740 --> 00:08:31,610
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

128
00:08:31,970 --> 00:08:34,860
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

129
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:36,820
Why did you buy me a hairpin?

130
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:40,140
That day, Grandmother
gave her gold hairpin to Bai Anyuan.

131
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:41,900
I'd like to give you one as well.

132
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,460
♪Now I gaze alone at the full moon,
entranced by its wistful beauty♪

133
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:45,020
I don't want you to be mistreated.

134
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,300
How does it look?

135
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,300
It's not as pretty as you.

136
00:08:58,620 --> 00:09:01,220
But Ms. Bai's hairpin was made of gold.

137
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,260
I risked my life
to suck the poison out for you,

138
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:06,460
yet all you gave me in return
was a silver hairpin.

139
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,700
I will give you all the beautiful things

140
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:11,020
that life has to offer from now on.

141
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:26,380
It is Meng's mother.

142
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:43,900
Are you all right?

143
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:14,650
♪Familiar yet strange sights♪

144
00:10:15,140 --> 00:10:17,570
♪The tale's first light♪

145
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:19,940
♪Growing with time's flow♪

146
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:23,480
♪Somber and mournful grief♪

147
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:26,770
♪The final act, my swan song as a bait♪

148
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:29,810
♪Has freed the heart from all desires♪

149
00:10:30,490 --> 00:10:34,810
♪As I dance with wolves,
love lies hidden deep♪

150
00:10:37,130 --> 00:10:41,690
♪The scented sachet,
a memory that never fades♪

151
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:46,890
♪With every passing day,
our love simmers and ignites♪

152
00:10:48,170 --> 00:10:51,050
♪The ache born
from our ephemeral meetings♪

153
00:10:51,650 --> 00:10:54,450
♪Etched upon the canvas of my heart♪

154
00:10:55,090 --> 00:10:59,490
♪How to untangle
this lasting, aching desire♪

155
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:03,850
♪In the face of such a bewitching gaze?♪

156
00:11:04,730 --> 00:11:10,250
♪Soft melodies caress locked windows,
reaching out to the setting sun♪

157
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:13,690
♪Gently adorning with twilight's charm♪

158
00:11:14,050 --> 00:11:16,690
♪My remaining breaths,
the thoughts that they bear♪

159
00:11:17,210 --> 00:11:21,690
♪The vision of you,
the one that fills my mind♪
